('3', 'chat_1768151864947_bWVlbmFAZ2_dkeemflni', 'I need to rent a bike', 'Renting a bike from NGN Motors is a great way to enjoy the freedom of the road! Here’s what you need to know about our bike rental services:\n\n### Rental Process\n1. **Choose Your Bike**: We offer a variety of motorcycles for rent. You can select based on your preference for style, size, and performance.\n2. **Rental Duration**: Decide how long you would like to rent the bike. We offer flexible rental periods to accommodate your needs.\n3. **Documentation**: You will need to provide a valid motorcycle license and identification. Make sure to have these ready when you come to rent.\n4. **Payment**: Payment can be made at the time of rental. We accept various payment methods for your convenience.\n\n### Benefits of Renting with Us\n- **Wide Selection**: We have a diverse range of motorcycles to meet different riding styles and preferences.\n- **Well-Maintained Bikes**: All our rental bikes are regularly serviced and maintained to ensure safety and reliability.\n- **Flexible Rental Terms**: Whether you need a bike for a day, a weekend, or longer, we can accommodate your needs.\n\n### Contact Us\nFor more detailed information about our rental options, including pricing and availability, please reach out to us:\n\n- **Catford**: **0208 314 1498**\n- **Tooting**: **0203 409 5478**\n- **Sutton**: **0208 412 9275**\n- **Email**: [enquiries@neguinhomotors.co.uk](mailto:enquiries@neguinhomotors.co.uk)\n\n### Hours of Operation\n- **Monday to Saturday**: 9 AM - 6 PM\n- **Sunday**: Closed\n\nFor more information, visit our [Rentals Information](/rentals-information) page. We look forward to helping you get on the road with one of our fantastic rental bikes!', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2026-01-13 20:41:41', '0', 'read', '2', 'meena', 'meena@gmail.com', NULL, '78.129.186.51', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/143.0.0.0', '{\"