('5', 'chat_1768151963157_c2VuanVqb3_5vyhm97zh', 'I need a bike', 'At NGN Motors, we offer a wide selection of motorcycles to suit various needs and preferences. Whether you\'re looking for a commuter bike, a sport bike, or something for off-road adventures, we have options available for you.\n\n### Motorcycle Sales\nYou can explore our extensive range of motorcycles in our [Motorcycle Sales](/motorcycle-sales) section. Here, you\'ll find detailed information about each model, including specifications, pricing, and availability. Our team is dedicated to helping you find the perfect bike that fits your lifestyle and budget.\n\n### Why Choose NGN Motors?\n- **Expert Advice**: Our knowledgeable staff can assist you in selecting the right motorcycle based on your experience level and intended use.\n- **Quality Assurance**: We ensure that all our bikes undergo thorough inspections for safety and performance.\n- **Financing Options**: We offer various financing plans to make your purchase more manageable.\n\n### Contact Us\nIf you have any questions or need further assistance, please don\'t hesitate to reach out. You can contact us via:\n\n- **Phone Numbers**:\n  - Catford: **0208 314 1498**\n  - Tooting: **0203 409 5478**\n  - Sutton: **0208 412 9275**\n  \n- **Email**: enquiries@neguinhomotors.co.uk\n\n### Visit Us\nOur operating hours are Monday to Saturday from **9 am to 6 pm**, and we are closed on Sundays. We invite you to visit our showroom to see our motorcycles in person and take a test ride.\n\nFeel free to check out our [Motorcycle Sales](/motorcycle-sales) page for more information and to view our current inventory. We look forward to helping you find the perfect bike!', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2026-01-13 20:38:42', '0', 'read', '2', 'Senju Jose', 'senjujose678@gmail.com', NULL, '185.164.138.72', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/143.0.0.0', '{\"model\":\"gpt-4o-mini-2024-07-18\",\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":646,\"completion_tokens\":355,\"total_tokens\":1001,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"accepted_prediction_tokens\":0,\"rejected_prediction_tokens\":0}},\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"truncated\":false}', '2026-01-11 17:53:58', '2026-01-13 20:38:42'),
('6', 'chat_1768151963157_c2VuanVqb3_5vyhm97zh', 'prices', 'To provide you with accurate pricing information, it would be helpful to know which specific service or product you are interested in. At NGN Motors, we offer various services, including motorcycle sales and rentals. Here’s a brief overview:\n\n### Motorcycle Sales\n- Prices for motorcycles can vary widely based on the make, model, year, and condition of the bike. We have a diverse selection of motorcycles available for sale. \n- For detailed pricing and to see our current inventory, please check our [Motorcycle Sales](/motorcycle-sales) page.\n\n### Rentals\n- Rental prices also depend on the type of motorcycle you wish to rent, the duration of the rental, and any additional services you may require.\n- For comprehensive rental pricing and options, visit our [Rentals Information](/rentals-information) page.\n\n### Contact Us\nIf you have specific questions or need assistance with pricing for a particular motorcycle or rental, feel free to reach out to us directly. Our team is ready to help you with any inquiries.\n\n- **Catford**: **0208 314 1498**\n- **Tooting**: **0203 409 5478**\n- **Sutton**: **0208 412 9275**\n- **Email**: enquiries@neguinhomotors.co.uk\n\n### Hours of Operation\n- **Monday-Saturday**: 9am - 6pm\n- **Sunday**: Closed\n\nPlease let us know how we can assist you further!', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2026-01-13 20:38:42', '0', 'read', '3', 'Senju Jose', 'senjujose678@gmail.com', NULL, '185.164.138.72', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/143.0.0.0', '{\"model\":\"gpt-4o-mini-2024-07-18\",\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":651,\"completion_tokens\":304,\"total_tokens\":955,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"accepted_prediction_tokens\":0,\"rejected_prediction_tokens\":0}},\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"truncated\":