('7', 'chat_1768151963157_c2VuanVqb3_5vyhm97zh', 'rent price', 'At NGN Motors, we offer a variety of rental options for motorcycles, but specific rental prices can vary based on the type of motorcycle, rental duration, and any additional services you may require. \n\n### Rental Pricing Overview:\n- **Motorcycle Type**: Different models have different pricing. For example, a standard commuter bike may cost less than a high-performance sport bike.\n- **Rental Duration**: Prices may vary depending on whether you are renting for a day, a week, or longer.\n- **Additional Services**: Optional add-ons like insurance or gear rental may also affect the total cost.\n\nTo get the most accurate and up-to-date pricing, I recommend checking our [Rentals Information](/rentals-information) page, where you can find detailed information about the available motorcycles and their respective rental prices.\n\n### Contact Us for More Information:\nIf you have specific questions or need assistance with your rental inquiry, please feel free to reach out to us:\n\n- **Catford**: **0208 314 1498**\n- **Tooting**: **0203 409 5478**\n- **Sutton**: **0208 412 9275**\n- **Email**: enquiries@neguinhomotors.co.uk\n\n### Hours of Operation:\n- **Monday-Saturday**: 9am-6pm\n- **Sunday**: Closed\n\nWe are here to help you find the perfect motorcycle rental that fits your needs!', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2026-01-13 20:38:42', '0', 'read', '4', 'Senju Jose', 'senjujose678@gmail.com', NULL, '185.164.138.72', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/143.0.0.0', '{\"model\":\"gpt-4o-mini-2024-07-18\",\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":653,\"completion_tokens\":296,\"total_tokens\":949,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"accepted_prediction_tokens\":0,\"rejected_prediction_tokens\":0}},\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"truncated\":false}'