('14', 'chat_1768265266257_aW10aWF6YW_a5h387yx8', 'I want to bike on instalments', 'At NGN Motors, we understand that purchasing a motorcycle can be a significant investment, and many customers prefer to explore financing options, including buying on instalments. While we currently do not have specific information regarding instalment plans directly available in our knowledge base, we encourage you to reach out to us for detailed assistance.\n\n### Here’s how you can get started:\n\n1. **Visit Our Motorcycle Sales Section**: Check out our [Motorcycle Sales](/motorcycle-sales) page to explore the range of motorcycles we offer. You can find various models that might suit your needs and budget.\n\n2. **Contact Us for Financing Options**: For specific information regarding instalment plans or financing options, please contact us directly. Our team will provide you with the necessary details and help you understand the available options.\n\n### Contact Information:\n- **Phone Numbers**:\n  - Catford: **0208 314 1498**\n  - Tooting: **0203 409 5478**\n  - Sutton: **0208 412 9275**\n- **Email**: enquiries@neguinhomotors.co.uk\n\n### Our Hours:\n- **Monday-Saturday**: 9am-6pm\n- **Sunday**: Closed\n\n### Additional Information:\nWhen you contact us, please have the following information ready to help us assist you better:\n- The specific motorcycle model you are interested in.\n- Your budget range for monthly payments.\n- Any additional questions regarding the purchasing process.\n\nWe look forward to helping you find the perfect motorcycle and assisting you with financing options that fit your needs!', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2026-01-13 20:38:43', '0', 'read', '2', 'Imtiaz Ahmed', 'imtiazahmedy37@gmail.com', NULL, '92.40.174.102', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Linux; Android 10; K) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Mobile Safari/537.36', '{\"model\":\"gpt-4o-mini-2024-07-18\",\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":652,\"completion_tokens\":324,\"total_tokens\":976,\"prompt_tok