('28', 'chat_1768339408194_am9zZUBnbW_tksgx9hvz', 'rental information', 'At NGN Motors, we offer a variety of rental options for motorcycles and e-bikes. Below is the detailed rental information available:\n\n### Rental Options and Prices\n\n1. **HONDA Vision 110 (2017)**\n   - **Rental Price**: £1.00/week\n   - **Deposit**: £200.00\n\n2. **NGN E-Bike (2025)**\n   - **Rental Price**: £60.00/week\n   - **Deposit**: £250.00\n\n3. **NGN EBIKE (2025)**\n   - **Rental Price**: £60.00/week\n   - **Deposit**: £250.00\n\n4. **NGN EBIKE (2025)**\n   - **Rental Price**: £70.00/week\n   - **Deposit**: £250.00\n\n5. **YAMAHA GPD125-A NMAX 125 ABS (2023)**\n   - **Rental Price**: £70.00/week\n   - **Deposit**: £200.00\n\n### Additional Information\n- **Rental Duration**: Rentals are typically charged on a weekly basis.\n- **Deposits**: A deposit is required for each rental, which is refundable upon the return of the vehicle in good condition.\n- **Availability**: It’s advisable to check for availability and make a reservation in advance, especially during peak seasons.\n\nFor more detailed information about our rentals, including terms and conditions, please visit our [Rentals Information](/rentals-information) page.\n\n### Contact Us\nIf you have any questions or would like to make a booking, feel free to reach out to us:\n\n- **Phone Numbers**:\n  - Catford: **0208 314 1498**\n  - Tooting: **0203 409 5478**\n  - Sutton: **0208 412 9275**\n  \n- **Email**: enquiries@neguinhomotors.co.uk\n\n### Business Hours\n- **Monday to Saturday**: 9am - 6pm\n- **Sunday**: Closed\n\nWe look forward to assisting you with your rental needs!', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2026-01-13 21:23:37', '0', 'read', '1', 'joe', 'jose@gmail.com', NULL, '185.164.138.72', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/143.0.0.0', '{\"model\":\"gpt-4o-mini-2024-07-18\",\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":1073,\"completion_tokens\":450,\"total_tokens\":1523,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"accepted_prediction_tokens\":0,\"rejected_prediction_tokens\":0}},\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"truncated\":false}', '2026-01-13 21:23:28', '2026-01-13 21:23:37'),
('29', 'chat_1768340381423_c2l5YXJhQG_xp0xm91uw', 'can I know about your finance options', 'At NGN Motors, we understand that financing is an important aspect when purchasing a motorcycle. While specific finance options may vary, we typically offer flexible financing solutions to help you acquire the motorcycle you desire.\n\n### Financing Options\n1. **Hire Purchase**: This option allows you to pay for the motorcycle in installments over a set period. You will own the motorcycle once all payments are made.\n   \n2. **Personal Contract Purchase (PCP)**: With this option, you pay a deposit followed by lower monthly payments. At the end of the term, you can choose to pay a final balloon payment to own the motorcycle, return it, or trade it in for a new model.\n\n3. **Personal Loans**: You may also consider taking out a personal loan from a bank or financial institution to purchase your motorcycle outright.\n\n### Benefits of Financing\n- **Affordability**: Spread the cost of your motorcycle over time, making it easier to manage your budget.\n- **Flexibility**: Choose a financing plan that suits your financial situation and preferences.\n- **Access to New Models**: Financing allows you to purchase a motorcycle that may be out of reach if paying upfront.\n\n### Next Steps\nFor detailed information about specific finance options available, including interest rates and terms, please contact us directly. Our team can provide personalized advice based on your circumstances.\n\n**Contact Information:**\n- **Phone Numbers**: \n  - Catford: **0208 314 1498**\n  - Tooting: **0203 409 5478**\n  - Sutton: **0208 412 9275**\n- **Email**: [enquiries@neguinhomotors.co.uk](mailto:enquiries@neguinhomotors.co.uk)\n\n**Hours**: Monday-Saturday 9am-6pm, Sunday Closed\n\nFeel free to reach out to us, and we will be happy to assist you with your financing needs!', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2026-01-15 16:06:22', '0', 'read', '1', 'siyara', 'siyara@gmail.com', NULL, '185.164.138.72', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/143.0.0.0', '{\"model\":\"gpt-4o-mini-2024-07-18\",\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":950,\"completion_tokens\":396,\"total_tokens\":1346,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0,\"accepted_prediction_tokens\":0,\"rejected_prediction_tokens\":0}},\"finish_reason\":\"stop\",\"truncated\":false}', '2026-01-13 21:39:43', '2026-01-15 16:06:22'),
('30', 'chat_1768340381423_c2l5YXJhQG_xp0xm91uw', 'rental options', 'At NGN Motors, we offer a variety of rental options for motorcycles and e-bikes. Below are the available rental choices along with their weekly prices and deposits:\n\n### Rental Options:\n\n1. **HONDA Vision 110 (2017)**\n   - **Rental Price:** £1.00/week\n   - **Deposit:** £200.00\n\n2. **NGN E-Bike (2025)**\n   - **Rental Price:** £60.00/week\n   - **Deposit:** £250.00\n\n3. **NGN EBIKE (2025)**\n   - **Rental Price:** £60.00/week\n   - **Deposit:** £250.00\n\n4. **NGN EBIKE (2025)**\n   - **Rental Price:** £70.00/week\n   - **Deposit:** £250.00\n\n5. **YAMAHA GPD125-A NMAX 125 ABS (2023)**\n   - **Rental Price:** £70.00/week\n   - **Deposit:** £200.00\n\n### Additional Information:\n- All rentals require a deposit, which is refundable upon the return of the vehicle in good condition.\n- Rental prices are subject to availability, so it\'s advisable to book in advance.\n\nFor more details about our rental options, please visit our [Rentals Information](/rentals-information) page.\n\n### Contact Us:\nIf you have any questions or would like to make a reservation, feel free to reach out to us via the following:\n\n- **Phone Numbers:**\n  - Catford: **0208 314 1498**\n  - Tooting: **0203 409 5478**\n  - Sutton: **0208 412 9275**\n\n- **Email:** enquiries@neguinhomotors.co.uk\n\n### Hours of Operation:\n- **Monday-Saturday:** 9am-6pm\n- **Sunday:** Closed\n\nWe look forward to assisting you with your rental needs!', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2026-01-15 16:06:22', '0', 'read', '2', 'siyara', 'siyara@gmail.com', NULL, '185.164.138.72', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/143.0.0.0', '{\"model\":\"gpt-4o-mini-2024-07-18\",\"usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":1073,\"completion_tokens\":408,\"total_tokens\":1481,\"prompt_tokens_details\":{\"cached_tokens\":0,\"audio_tokens\":0},\"completion_tokens_details\":{\"reasoning_tokens\":0,\"aud